  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nThe backend fully exist, only QML part has to be implemented. Shouldn't take more than 2 hours.\r\nThere's a separate `ConentType = SystemMessagePinnedMessage`. `pinnedBy` and `responseTo` are good to use here.\r\n\r\nThis requires design first.\r\n\r\nCurrent implementation is a non-interactive text.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"851\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/25482501/235657887-cc340ba3-6609-4a70-9f7b-87123342f739.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Discord behaviour\r\n\r\n#### System notification\r\n\r\n<img width=\"370\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/25482501/235657232-3d32b4cc-c235-4509-8297-13eb06b203f4.png\">\r\n\r\n#### Chat\r\n\r\n* The message is hoverable\r\n* Username, \"message\" and \"pinned messages\" are clickable links\r\n* Possible to create reactions to the system message\r\n\r\n<img width=\"840\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/25482501/235657429-34567c55-adf4-446c-877d-01f115fba201.png\">",
